data.description: This updated ranch home, situated on 10 private acres with a long driveway and stock pond, offers a perfect blend of comfort and convenience! As you step inside, you're welcome by an inviting open-concept living and kitchen area, featuring a woodburner that creates a cozy atmosphere.  With 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, including a fully finished basement, this home provides ample space for comfortable living! The recent updates ensure that you can move in with a peace of mind. A new furnace and AC system, along with a new hot water tank and whole house reverse osmosis system, offer modern efficiency. Outside, a new pole barn (30x50 with 12x16 overhang) provides additional storage or workspace, while the new septic and well systems guarantee reliability for years to come. Additionally, there is a portable generator hookup and new electrical panel. Whether you're seeking tranquility in the countryside or a welcoming retreat to call home, this property has everything you need!
